MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 1335

CREATING AND DESIGNATING THE METROPOLIS STAR LOCATED ALONG SOUTH SUPER HIGHWAY, ALABANG, MUNTINLUPA CITY, METRO MANILA, AS INFORMATION TECHNOLOGY CENTER PURSUANT TO REPUBLIC ACT NO. 7916 AS AMENDED BY REPUBLIC ACT NO. 8748

Pursuant to the powers vested in me under Republic Act No. 7916, the Special Economic Zone Act of 1995 as amended by Republic Act No. 8748 and upon recommendation of the Board of Directors of the Philippine Economic Zone Authority, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO , President of the Republic of the Philippines, do hereby create and designate as Information Technology Center, subject to the provisions of Republic Act No. 7916 as amended, its Implementing Rules and Regulations, and Resolutions Nos. 00-411 and 05-416 dated 29 December 2000 and 28 November 2005, respectively, of the Board of Directors of the Philippine Economic Zone Authority (PEZA), the Metropolis Star, which was established on a lot located along South Super Highway, Alabang, Muntinlupa City, Metro Manila, containing an area of FIFTY ONE THOUSAND NINE HUNDRED TWENTY EIGHT (51,928) SQUARE METERS , more or less, as defined by the following technical descriptions:

Lot 1 Pcs-00-012172

A parcel of land (Lot 1 of the consolidation-subdivision plan, Pcs-00-012172, being a portion of the consolidation of Lots 177-B & C, (LRC) Psd-43896; Lot 184, Swo-12647; Lots 178, 183, Muntinlupa Estate; Lot 1335-B, Psd-28392; Lots 2-A to 2-D, (LRC) Psd-321042; Lot 1 (LRC) Pcs-1213; Lots 1 & 2, Pcs-04-000126; Lots 10-E-3-A-1, (LRC) Psd-326068; Lot 10-E-1 & Lot 10-E-2, (LRC) Psd-270570; Lots 1332-E-1-B to E, (LRC) Psd-303349; Lot 1332-A-1-A & Lot 1332-A-1-B, (LRC) Psd-301416, LRC Record No. 6137), situated in Barangay of Alabang, City of Muntinlupa, Metro Manila, Island of Luzon.

